{"tid":1485553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"捉鬼係另類分化 此風不可長","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T16:16:11.000Z","uid":222643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"115b77e5579c8240a93ebfeffd67018cff0a4581","tid":1485553,"uid":222643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:12:07.000Z","msg":"我唔理依家版上面屌個d係假膠, 三毛定和理非<br />\n言論都犯左大忌, 今晚黎講大量言論標籤<br />\n仲留既就係鬼<br />\n仲留既就浪費遊行人士今晚既付出<br />\n想營造一種留 = 鬼, 鬼先會留, 嘗試製造割席風向, 並將此風向帶到之後每次遊行既後續<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔係三毛同假膠,<br />\n1. 如果你認為留係現場只係得番鬼, 你唔使講咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 如果留係現場有手足有鬼, 手足自有判斷, 你響度鬧唔會幫到件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 如果留係現場既係真手足, 有鬼呢樣野已經通哂天, 現場手足自有判斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要勸就好聲好氣d, 下下將留既都標籤成鬼只會步2014捉鬼後塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />此風不可長"},{"pid":"49a9e18df8ba36c067f90f5cb3de6535c2c1ba12","tid":1485553,"uid":222643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:15:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52dcad6fd68416f3557f833e2baf74259a184be","tid":1485553,"uid":222643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}